About the Series:
A series of three two-part stories.

Rose Linden(Sarah Lancashire) and Maloney(Phil Davis) work with the fictional Criminal Justice Review Agency,
an organization which seeks out miscarriages of justice. Rose is brilliant but strong-willed and sometimes 
reckless. She likes to follow her instincts and play hunches and often comes into conflict with authority. 
Maloney, although Rose's superior, usually allows himself to be led by his more passionate colleague. 
Maloney is a by-the-book man and a little grey. He finds working with Rose dangerous but addictively 
exciting.
